To setup on your host, you need to add:
www-data ALL=NOPASSWD: /srv/web/build.webconverger.com/build.sh
to /etc/sudoers

Thanks to Ben Armstrong & Chris Lamb for their comments.

The build script has to be run in a terminal (not via CGI or CRON) because of a
xfonts-scalable bug: http://bugs.debian.org/cgi-bin/bugreport.cgi?bug=498189

# Crontab contents:

@daily sudo /srv/web/build.webconverger.com/runme.sh
@daily find /srv/web/build.webconverger.com/imgs -mindepth 1 -maxdepth 1 -ctime +4 -exec rm -vrf {} \;
